title: Front Cover
content: A nesting yellow-eyed penguin (Megadyptes antipodes) in the subantarctic Auckland Islands. The cover image relates to Research Article https://doi.org/10.1002/aqc.4143 “Variable breeding success and its implication in the conservation of endangered yellow-eyed penguin (Megadyptes antipodes) at the New Zealand subantarctic Auckland Islands” by Muller et al.
